<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"title-1"><br>Mean, median, mode and ra=
nge in math curriculum</h3>



<p>It is useful for students to be aware of mean, median, mode and range de=
spite it not being an explicit requirement, as an introduction at this stag=
e proves useful for later years. When dealing with data that contains outli=
ers, finding the mean may not always be the best option.</p>



